Issue located manually.
Issue found in Excel sheet, 'QIV3-CHU HI', cell P22. This is empty for 'no value'.
Excel interprets an empty cell as '0' so the calculation in Q22 yeilds '0'. This then
carries on to cell R22 interpreted as a 'non-responder' where it is in fact a 'unknown value'.

In summary, subject CHU-017 is not a 'non-responder' but rather an 'unknown'.
The error is with Excel interpreting an empty cell as '0'.

